  "keyFeatures": [
    "Offline-first architecture — all notes stored and editable locally",
    "Automatic cross-device sync when online",
    "Rich text editor with formatting, headings, lists, and checkboxes",
    "Note sharing with viewer or editor permissions",
    "Tags with custom colors for organization",
    "Pin, archive, and trash notes with soft-delete recovery",
    "OIDC authentication (Pocket ID, Authelia, Keycloak, etc.)",
    "Self-hostable via Docker with embedded or external PostgreSQL",
    "Admin panel for user management, registration control, and system stats",
    "Flutter-based Android mobile app with offline support"
  ],
